abstract: >-
  An AI-powered chatbot for answering soil-related questions,
  developed as part of the European SoilWise project. It integrates
  with the SoilWise catalog, ISRIC SoilGrids, agricultural field
  data services, and soil vocabulary resources to provide
  comprehensive soil information.
